snippet.title: Boom Chick Chick [www.silverdollargames.com]
snippet.description: Use a series of satisfying weapons to annihilate hordes of monsters in this unique single stick shooter.  Experience 4 levels of difficulty, up to 4 player coop, local highscores, and a killer soundtrack courtesy of Razorback Records.  Boom Chick Chick its music to my ears.
